    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="col-md-6 fade-in">
      <div class="about-card">
        <h2 class="title">About Me</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          I have been teaching private piano lessons since 1993. In addition to 
          teaching, I am also active as an accompanist and freelance musician.
        </p>

        <p class="about-text">
          I teach children age 5 and up, as well as adults of all skill levels 
          from beginners through early advanced students.
        </p>

        <p class="about-text">
          I hold a master’s degree in Piano Pedagogy from Columbus State University 
          and have completed post-graduate studies in piano accompanying.
        </p>

        <p class="about-text">
          In addition to private teaching, I have taught early childhood music 
          classes and university-level courses for both credit and non-credit programs.
        </p>
